# Implementation Checklist
## Step-by-Step Build Guide

Use this checklist to track your progress building the dashboard.

---

## Phase 1: Preparation ⏭️

- [ ] **Step 1.1** — Create a new Google Sheet file
  - Go to https://sheets.google.com
  - Click "Create" → "Spreadsheet"
  - Name it: "Keystone Acquisitions - New Leads Dashboard"
  
- [ ] **Step 1.2** — Rename the default sheet
  - Right-click "Sheet1"
  - Rename to: "Leads Database"

- [ ] **Step 1.3** — Create the dashboard sheet
  - Click "+" to add a new sheet
  - Name it: "New Leads Dashboard"

- [ ] **Step 1.4** — Review your lead data source
  - Identify where your current leads are stored
  - Plan how to migrate/copy data to "Leads Database" sheet

