## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Formulas show #ERROR | Check sheet name is exactly "Leads Database" |
| FILTER formulas don't work | Ensure you're using Google Sheets (not Excel) |
| KPI values don't update | Click recalculate (Ctrl+Shift+F9) or wait a moment |
| Charts don't show data | Verify data range is correct and includes headers |
| Conditional formatting not showing | Check condition rules are set correctly and formatting is applied |
| Last Updated time is old | Formulas recalculate when the sheet changes; force with F9 |

